title: Logansquare 2 bedroom garden unit,laundry. Great location on Blvd
posting_body: Logan Square garden apartment each bedroom can fit a queen size bed and dresser.
- the kitchen and living room are smaller It is full of sunlight as it is a corner unit .
Six minute walk to the el.
Surrounded by great restaurants, bars ,blues clubs art galleries etc.
Me for fast response I can show any day at 2:30 if good text me 30 minutes before to confirm.
When you are communicating please say you are calling  about the two bedroom garden apartment.
Btw There is also a loft available for the same price let me know if you want to see pictures on that one.
